# SVG icon files (if you ever extract the inline SVGs out of the HTML).
#
# By default the site uses inline SVGs for social and UI icons (Facebook,
# Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, chevrons, close X, stars). They're inline
# so they pick up `currentColor` for hover states and don't need an extra
# HTTP request.
#
# This folder is reserved for any standalone SVG/icon assets you want to
# add later — favicons, custom logo marks, etc.
